<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/218383-had-been-reading-for-about-last-two-month">Had been reading for about last two month. Book starts out well and collects itself together in the end (I&#39;m almost done). However, it get&#39;s too scattered in the middle due to introduction of many MM personnel, cities/places and art pieces. Not really an exciting read but still a good book nevertheless. :) Good reads says my question requires a question mark, really? :D</a>
</div>
