<div class='bookAuthorProfile__photoContainer'>
<a href="/author/show/66216.Robert_M_Edsel"><div class='bookAuthorProfile__photo' style='background-image: url(https://images.gr-assets.com/authors/1390584158p3/66216.jpg);'></div>
